{"tid":1304454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奉勸各位，切勿過分留戀連儂牆","createTime":"2019-07-10T15:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T17:13:07.000Z","uid":154702,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b4a088ab3fa585e73a1860e83bd89c52cb42a54e","tid":1304454,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:20:20.000Z","msg":"負皮之前請聽小弟一言<br />\n冇錯連儂牆係有佢嘅作用<br />\n我絕對無意否定連儂牆既存在價值<br />\n的而且確有好多市民或者義士透過此而提醒到自己並不孤單，透過字條得到唔同嘅訊息<br />\n就好似將大家嘅支持同埋鼓勵<br />\n響唔同社區裏面實體化一樣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但此絕對唔應該成為抗爭嘅主體</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n連儂牆只係抗爭裏面嘅一座燈塔<br />\n透過燈光我哋見到大家，見到戰友<br />\n知道自己並不孤單，係重要嘅<br />\n但係絕對唔適合用黎留戀<br />\n（雖然視覺上的確好震撼好靚好吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n冇錯敵對陣營係會黎破壞<br />\n都理解到大家會覺得好可惜<br />\n但係真心建議睇開啲<br />\n因為破壞總比建設容易<br />\n焦點失衡係為敵方提供打開破口既機會<br />\n寧願多啲響網絡文宣上面投放人力同時間<br />\n<br />\n再者<br />\n抗爭嘅主體應該係大家嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">行動力</span></strong><br />\n透過每次行動向政府施壓反抗<br />\n記唔記得，令到政府最頭痛嘅係我哋be water ?<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有大台，抗爭過後散入城市之中<br />\n各自整備迎合下一次行動</span></strong><br />\n但連儂牆就剛好同我地既be water 優勢相反<br />\n企定定響一個地方等人哋黎攻佔<br />\n<br />\n請大家唔好忘記烈士係為乜嘢而死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>毋忘五大訴求<br />\n毋忘初衷<br />\n不撤不散<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"0a6a1f667145135bfeb3566d5fd5ba984d017075","tid":1304454,"uid":1655,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:21:05.000Z","msg":"連儂牆真係守唔過，因為連儂牆既特色就係即使俾人拆左第二日都會出現返"},{"pid":"4f5dc7a19186fdda8c571fe3870b1083586344a8","tid":1304454,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a6a1f667145135bfeb3566d5fd5ba984d017075","tid":1304454,"uid":1655,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:21:05.000Z","msg":"連儂牆真係守唔過，因為連儂牆既特色就係即使俾人拆左第二日都會出現返"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:21:46.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"317c9ec583bcc42c323688752ca9ea871ed7a5f0","tid":1304454,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:22:08.000Z","msg":"岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6ecda8643980032716fa0c040e5b8837236684","tid":1304454,"uid":129243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"Agger 唔需要比機會人攻"},{"pid":"0dd5d39b678e94af9d6dc8b53d3ff6f5e2d3ce75","tid":1304454,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:32:42.000Z","msg":"流濃牆根本就係寫大字報咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">寫重點</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁鐘意整靚靚返屋企寫係fb/ig 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481d2694777e05dbf74fe01f8c7175b4b218df86","tid":1304454,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:32:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fd2e0e67968d4b55f5fe29623286a2d79be003a4","tid":1304454,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:34:14.000Z","msg":"啱，廢老要撕嘅，我地要佢撕到手都廢為止，唔好為咗一幅牆而比位狗入"},{"pid":"79d50886067720c5e24c9309d28225fc5444e4c2","tid":1304454,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:36:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1dbfa2b47bb16f9cce041cbd5f3b95c2f6a3d6f0","tid":1304454,"uid":119610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"推呀，又話be water, 但又成日都死守某啲嘢做乜啫，反正都拆一貼十架啦"},{"pid":"b33c95eb5e20a079867076eb8d294b248bc84914","tid":1304454,"uid":268596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:39:00.000Z","msg":"重申抗爭所堅持之五大訴求:<br />\n一、撤回修例<br />\n二、撤回6.12暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、責成獨立調查委員會追究警方濫權<br />\n五、實行雙真普選<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pa2CgnD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpa2CgnD.png&h=acdc5205&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3514c4b0115e19934fd8e150862ca6ce0a1cc5d","tid":1304454,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:55:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cafc8005129d631a99f95b18c6d1b4d1b9aa41a3","tid":1304454,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:10:23.000Z","msg":"自己推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faeea33c40cf7b8d8e168c42a6fb80a605df1b25","tid":1304454,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T23:21:43.000Z","msg":"牆可以再起，但香港無左就無左<br />\n各位be water"},{"pid":"be68917c597b4a9b31247a79bbb83d140643cc8b","tid":1304454,"uid":159913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T23:22:33.000Z","msg":"支線任務嚟，勿硬碰<br />\n============================<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\n【團結】無大台嘅抗爭，我哋應該無時無刻激烈咁互屌。但冷靜之後要記得我哋係同路人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1305309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1305309</a></span>"},{"pid":"0daed1b615cf47ebecb6b18d7a6b196e0400cf9e","tid":1304454,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:25:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"696dc965bd3783a86dd89da7639f04af04935a1e","tid":1304454,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:10:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54ca642f6cb243f7112db1d9f0573ce8b3d5fac1","tid":1304454,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:13:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">立即停手，我而家嚴重警告你，唔好再襲擊<br />\n<br />\n我而家係制止你再打人，請立即停手<br />\n<br />\n我而家係公民拘捕你，因為你對我朋友施以實質傷害的襲擊</span></strong></span>"}]}